om/content/images/wordpress/2022/08/nemo-tweaks.png" alt="17 Dolphin File Manager Tips and Tweaks for KDE Users"></div></a></figure><p> I hope you find these tips helpful in getting more out of KDE.</p><p> Please share your questions and suggestions in the comments.</p> ; 
